### ============================================================
### 01. 토큰 발급
### ============================================================
### [사전 조건] erp-organization 이 정상 기동된 상태
###   - DefaultRoleInitializer: ADMIN, EMPLOYEE 역할 생성
###   - AdminInitializer: admin 계정 생성
### ============================================================

### admin 토큰 발급
# > 응답 access_token → http-client.env.json admin_token 에 복사
POST http://localhost:8180/realms/modu-erp/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=admin-cli&username=admin&password=admin

### 임직원 토큰 발급 (등록 후 사용)
# username / password 를 실제 등록한 값으로 교체
POST http://localhost:8180/realms/modu-erp/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=admin-cli&username=<employee_email>&password=<employee_password>
